[cron:e8c8a969-954b-4103-9515-1be9b365351c Weekly Hot Stocks Scanner] Run the Hot Scanner for stocks and crypto. Execute: cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/stock-analysis && python3 scripts/hot_scanner.py --json. Analyze trending stocks and crypto. ALSO do web searches for: 1) Weekly Asian market summary (Nikkei, Shanghai, Kospi, Hang Seng) 2) European/London markets weekly (FTSE, DAX, commodities) 3) US market weekly outlook 4) Fed/political events affecting markets. For each trending pick, provide: 1) Ticker 2) Current price 3) Price targets for each timeframe (1 day, 2 days, 5 days, 1-2 weeks) 4) Entry points 5) Risk assessment. Factor in Wyckoff cycle analysis and global market context. Deliver actionable weekly trades.
Current time: Sunday, February 22nd, 2026 — 10:37 AM (America/New_York)

Return your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself.
